rqt_console:
logging archtecture to display output from nodes

useful to monitor whats going on between nodes

# open log console, which will print the messages (and let you manage it)
rosrun rqt_console rqt_console

$ open the logger level. Allows you to select which level of messages will be printed
rosrun rqt_logger_level rqt_logger_level

the logger level follows the hierarchy below to print messages:
Fatal - most important
Error
Warn
Info
Debug

if you select debug, all other messages will also be printed. If error is selected, only error and fatal messages will be printed

reference:
http://wiki.ros.org/ROS/Tutorials/UsingRqtconsoleRoslaunch